2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the use of deep learning methods for image classification and compares the performance of modified models with the original. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper uses deep neural networks for image classification tasks, which falls under the domain of AI. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper discusses the ResNeXt model architecture, which is a type of neural network. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper may involve discussions on the data structures and algorithms used for implementing and evaluating the ResNeXt model architecture.
